{"tid":524451,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係地鐵度重遇多年前暗戀對象，偷望多左兩眼，女友係隔離知道左要分手","createTime":"2018-01-09T14:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T11:09:28.000Z","uid":66833,"like":4,"dislike":342,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"e30350791dd8104b47eeca79b5e94aaaaffefdbc","tid":524451,"uid":66833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:55:40.000Z","msg":"前日係地鐵度同女友番緊屋企，剛好就見到同樣番屋企既前暗戀對象，以前都幾熟，但而家已經好多年無見，Msg 都係隔幾個月先有兩幾句講下。<br />\n簡單講兩句後佢行開左，之後隔一陣我回頭偷望左兩眼。<br />\n<br />\n落車時因為同路關係，我想同女友同個女仔一齊行，順便講多幾句，了解下大家近況。女友示意想行另一邊而唔想一齊行但我忽視左。<br />\n<br />\n之後女友勁唔開心，話要分手，巴絲點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：呢個暗戀既女仔係我初戀前既事，我同初戀一齊後已對呢個女仔無哂感覺。呢次地鐵相遇係好多年無見後第一次見番。我真係好喜歡而家既女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9bb69dc8f68910aebd6e313db847a3525f4524","tid":524451,"uid":63721,"like":248,"dislike":6,"score":242,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"女朋友係你隔離都仲要咁 抵你死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13275b967d6ab17584cf2036256883e02a341f20","tid":524451,"uid":66833,"like":5,"dislike":30,"score":-25,"quote":{"pid":"ae9bb69dc8f68910aebd6e313db847a3525f4524","tid":524451,"uid":63721,"like":248,"dislike":6,"score":242,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"女朋友係你隔離都仲要咁 抵你死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T15:00:02.000Z","msg":"我知錯啦，我對佢無意思但行為上既表現就唔係咁，我知錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d5cffc6e2ec28c9b90d2ddeb0d87c5928ef094","tid":524451,"uid":57776,"like":63,"dislike":2,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T15:02:36.000Z","msg":"鬼叫你係女朋友面前都要咁咩，仲要一齊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cla